def pred_img(img):
    im = cv2.imread(img)
    resize = tf.image.resize(im,(256,256))
    yhat = model.predict(np.expand_dims(resize/255,0))
    print(yhat)
    if (yhat >= 0.5):
        print("Real")
    else:
        print("Ai Generated")
